data.description: Escape the hustle & bustle to enjoy the tranquility of mountain living at an elevation of 2770. Tucked away so you can unwind & reconnect with family & nature. The immaculate cabin offers the perfect blend of nature & comfort. The 3-bed, 3-bath layout ensures ample space and privacy for residents or guests, with a bathroom conveniently located on each level. Pull-in garage & carport for parking multiple vehicles. Walkable park-like setting perfect for nature lovers. Whether you are looking for a full-time residence, second home, or vacation rental property this cabin is adaptable to your needs.
